This unit is a boot time helper with a simple modus operandi: Load the specified
sector on specified drive and make the input feed from it and the following
sectors. The feed never stops and has to be stopped from the code it interprets.

## API

secload ( fromsec drv -- )
  Allocate enough space for reading one sector from "drv", then switch the input
  stream to the beginning of "fromsec" on "drv". Whenever we reach the end of
  a sector, we load the subsequent one and continue from there, forever.
